data.description: This home is absolutely MOVE-IN ready!! It’s a beautiful 3 bed 1.5 bath home completely remodeled! Walk in and immediately see the new flooring throughout with fresh paint and completely updated kitchen with new Sink, back splash, cabinets and brand new appliances. Bathrooms are all new giving it a very modern look. The master bedroom is spacious with a huge walk-in closet! The home also has brand new central air unit! Outside you will find a nice size yard and a brand new deck with a freshly painted garage door! The roof, windows, and siding are all less than 4 years old.
